{"word":"G1986 - ἐπισπάομαι - epispáomai - ep-ee-spah'-om-ahee - Become uncircumcised","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπισπάομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epispáomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-spah'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Become uncircumcised</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விருத்தசேதனம் செய்"},{"paragraph":"to (attempt to) conceal circumcision"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G4685 - σπάω - spáō - spah'-o/4685\">G4685</a>; to <i>draw over</i>, that is, (with <a href=\"#/G203 - ἀκροβυστία - akrobystía - ak-rob-oos-tee'-ah/203\">G203</a> implied) <i>efface</i> the mark of <i>circumcision</i> (by recovering with the foreskin): - become uncircumcised.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}